I"y<p>Chen Wang is currently a postdoctoral fellow with the Robotics Institute at Carnegie Mellon University (CMU). He received the B.Eng. degree in Electrical Engineering from Beijing Institute of Technology (BIT) in 2014 and Ph.D. degree in Electrical Engineering from Nanyang Technological University (NTU) Singapore in 2019. His research interests include robot perception, vision, and machine learning.</p>

